## Conventions

This repository follows the shared **[Repo Standard](REPO-STANDARD.md)**
(agent entrypoint + Diátaxis docs + MADR decisions). New
contributors and agents should read [`AGENTS.md`](AGENTS.md) first, then
[`REPO-STANDARD.md`](REPO-STANDARD.md) for the layout.

## Documentation

Durable documentation lives in [`docs/`](docs/README.md), organized by Diátaxis:
tutorials, how-to guides, reference, and explanation. Decisions are recorded as
ADRs in [`docs/decisions/adrs/`](docs/decisions/adrs/README.md).
